567
00:33:28,070 --> 00:33:29,320
Is that the truth?

568
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:39,959
Gao Ping, Li Shu,

569
00:33:40,909 --> 00:33:42,428
I really didn't expect you two

570
00:33:42,429 --> 00:33:43,640
to be of this character.

571
00:33:44,390 --> 00:33:46,360
You collaborated to deceive someone

572
00:33:46,630 --> 00:33:47,948
to this extent.

573
00:33:47,949 --> 00:33:49,600
Not to mention,
you blackmailed for money.

574
00:33:50,070 --> 00:33:51,759
Do you still have any conscience?

575
00:33:52,150 --> 00:33:54,159
Do you know morals?

576
00:33:55,189 --> 00:33:56,400
No matter what the dispute is,

577
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:59,719
emotional or financial,

578
00:34:00,070 --> 00:34:01,919
it must be resolved within three days.

579
00:34:03,229 --> 00:34:05,040
Do not ruin the reputation
of our programme!

580
00:34:06,989 --> 00:34:08,040
I'm leaving first.

581
00:34:22,389 --> 00:34:23,880
Are you happy now?

582
00:34:32,590 --> 00:34:34,160
Why should I be happy?

583
00:34:36,150 --> 00:34:37,639
I am a victim here.

584
00:34:37,749 --> 00:34:39,280
What am I happy about?

585
00:34:40,430 --> 00:34:42,999
I just want my money back.

586
00:34:46,309 --> 00:34:48,240
I am also getting used.

587
00:34:48,789 --> 00:34:50,479
Shouldn't I take the money?

588
00:34:51,709 --> 00:34:52,559
I'm gonna tell you

589
00:34:52,749 --> 00:34:54,160
what you told me.

590
00:34:55,229 --> 00:34:56,880
'For every grievance, there's a source.'

591
00:34:57,430 --> 00:34:59,079
Your creditor is right here.

592
00:35:16,669 --> 00:35:17,519
How did it go?

593
00:35:19,990 --> 00:35:21,639
I said everything I wanted.

594
00:35:22,950 --> 00:35:24,599
I definitely want the money back.

595
00:35:25,189 --> 00:35:26,069
As for how the programme

596
00:35:26,070 --> 00:35:29,599
is going to punish him, he deserves it.

597
00:35:30,470 --> 00:35:31,959
Care about reputation?

598
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:33,999
It's not that easy.

599
00:35:35,269 --> 00:35:36,029
In fact, giving him a punishment

600
00:35:36,030 --> 00:35:37,240
is actually a bargain to him.

601
00:35:37,990 --> 00:35:40,400
I watched Mr. Lu coming out
with an angered face.

602
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:42,439
He must be furious.

603
00:35:43,749 --> 00:35:45,240
An old, reputable professor,

604
00:35:45,990 --> 00:35:48,840
who abstains from cigarettes and alcohol
and known for his rigorous teaching,

605
00:35:48,869 --> 00:35:50,360
must have really fallen on hard times

606
00:35:50,510 --> 00:35:52,439
to have encountered such a student.

607
00:35:53,389 --> 00:35:54,559
What did you say?

608
00:35:55,389 --> 00:35:56,280
What's wrong?

609
00:35:57,349 --> 00:35:58,919
Mr. Lu doesn't drink?

610
00:35:59,910 --> 00:36:01,519
That is what my friend said.

611
00:36:02,829 --> 00:36:04,720
Can you help me to confirm this?

612
00:36:05,269 --> 00:36:06,320
What's wrong?

613
00:36:07,030 --> 00:36:07,788
Do you remember the day

614
00:36:07,789 --> 00:36:09,200
you accompanied me
to the police station?

615
00:36:09,470 --> 00:36:10,868
It's the day Qi and Cong

616
00:36:10,869 --> 00:36:12,599
got lost with Ms. Zhang.

617
00:36:13,789 --> 00:36:14,999
When we went back,

618
00:36:15,309 --> 00:36:16,800
Gao Ping told me...

619
00:36:17,950 --> 00:36:19,280
Where were you in the afternoon?

620
00:36:22,150 --> 00:36:22,989
Prof. Yang

621
00:36:22,990 --> 00:36:24,268
made an appointment with Mr. Lu

622
00:36:24,269 --> 00:36:26,519
from the doctoral programme for lunch.

623
00:36:26,910 --> 00:36:28,308
Mr. Lu loves drinking

624
00:36:28,309 --> 00:36:30,119
so I had a few drinks with them

625
00:36:30,389 --> 00:36:31,400
and got drunk.

626
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,959
That jerk.

627
00:36:35,189 --> 00:36:36,800
I wonder how many lies he told.

628
00:36:51,269 --> 00:36:55,200
I went to that friend of mine
to confirm this.

629
00:36:55,990 --> 00:36:58,360
Mr. Lu has a bad liver

630
00:36:59,430 --> 00:37:01,160
so he gave up drinking a few years ago.

631
00:37:02,150 --> 00:37:03,800
Besides, guess what he said?

632
00:37:04,470 --> 00:37:06,188
Mr. Lu had a meeting

633
00:37:06,189 --> 00:37:08,119
in Xiamen on March 11th.

634
00:37:08,389 --> 00:37:09,959
He wasn't even in Shanghai.

635
00:37:24,950 --> 00:37:26,308
Is there something going on

636
00:37:26,309 --> 00:37:27,720
that prompted you
to suddenly call us out?

637
00:37:32,430 --> 00:37:35,240
It's about your sister and Gao Ping.

638
00:37:35,269 --> 00:37:36,629
I was with her on the day

639
00:37:36,630 --> 00:37:38,639
she checked the dashcam footage

640
00:37:38,950 --> 00:37:40,360
of their family car, right?

641
00:37:40,669 --> 00:37:41,868
We found out

642
00:37:41,869 --> 00:37:43,439
that their car was parked

643
00:37:43,470 --> 00:37:46,439
in a hotel for a long time.

644
00:37:46,869 --> 00:37:47,909
I happen to have a friend

645
00:37:47,910 --> 00:37:48,708
working there

646
00:37:48,709 --> 00:37:49,509
so your sister asked me

647
00:37:49,510 --> 00:37:50,439
to ask my friend about it.

648
00:37:52,470 --> 00:37:53,840
However, after asking,

649
00:37:56,550 --> 00:37:57,800
we found this.

650
00:38:03,309 --> 00:38:04,228
The two of them

651
00:38:04,229 --> 00:38:06,240
entered the hotel around 12 am

652
00:38:06,349 --> 00:38:07,999
and they came out around 6 am.

653
00:38:08,269 --> 00:38:09,559
Gosh.

654
00:38:10,910 --> 00:38:12,400
What a scumbag.

655
00:38:12,550 --> 00:38:13,999
I've seen this woman before.

656
00:38:15,430 --> 00:38:16,479
Who is she?

657
00:38:17,070 --> 00:38:18,599
I don't know who she is,

658
00:38:18,950 --> 00:38:20,228
but I told Xiang Qian

659
00:38:20,229 --> 00:38:21,880
that I saw this woman

660
00:38:22,030 --> 00:38:22,629
sitting in Gao Ping's car

661
00:38:22,630 --> 00:38:24,079
when I was crossing the street
on a random day.

662
00:38:31,789 --> 00:38:32,828
When I told Xiang Qian about it,

663
00:38:32,829 --> 00:38:33,959
she wasn't bothered.

664
00:38:35,749 --> 00:38:37,840
Gao Ping actually cheated on her.

665
00:38:39,749 --> 00:38:41,360
That's disgusting.

666
00:38:46,070 --> 00:38:47,240
This is

667
00:38:49,269 --> 00:38:50,519
your sister's family affair,

668
00:38:50,709 --> 00:38:53,519
but as a friend,

669
00:38:53,829 --> 00:38:54,959
I can't just ignore it.

670
00:38:54,990 --> 00:38:55,999
So

671
00:38:56,590 --> 00:38:59,240
I asked you two to meet to discuss

672
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:01,800
how to talk to your sister.

673
00:39:09,990 --> 00:39:11,069
Come on, stop looking at it.

674
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:12,280
You should eat.

675
00:39:13,630 --> 00:39:14,708
My eyes

676
00:39:14,709 --> 00:39:16,800
are starting to see double.

677
00:39:17,269 --> 00:39:19,039
They all look alike to me.

678
00:39:19,749 --> 00:39:21,039
Let me do it.

679
00:39:21,189 --> 00:39:22,069
Look,

680
00:39:22,070 --> 00:39:23,308
could this be Li Shu's alt account?

681
00:39:23,309 --> 00:39:24,400
Let me see.

682
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:26,509
(Hemeng Nana's Weibo)

683
00:39:26,510 --> 00:39:27,268
This...

684
00:39:27,269 --> 00:39:28,989
(Bit by bit I'm lowering
my expectations of you.)

685
00:39:28,990 --> 00:39:31,549
The address is correct

686
00:39:31,550 --> 00:39:34,760
but it doesn't seem like her.

687
00:39:35,910 --> 00:39:36,919
See?

688
00:39:36,950 --> 00:39:38,039
I'll take a look again.

689
00:39:41,950 --> 00:39:43,029
What time is it?

690
00:39:43,030 --> 00:39:43,868
You should go back.

691
00:39:43,869 --> 00:39:45,240
Jiang must be worried.

692
00:39:45,669 --> 00:39:47,479
It's fine. I already told him.

693
00:39:51,229 --> 00:39:51,629
By the way,

694
00:39:51,630 --> 00:39:52,469
have you completed

695
00:39:52,470 --> 00:39:53,840
the divorce procedures
with Deng Haiyang?

696
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:54,919
Yes.

697
00:39:55,349 --> 00:39:56,429
I've been busy for the past two days.

698
00:39:56,430 --> 00:39:58,160
I didn't even have time to tell you.

699
00:40:02,070 --> 00:40:04,039
How do you feel now?

700
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:05,360
Do you feel sad?

701
00:40:07,349 --> 00:40:09,549
When I just did it,

702
00:40:09,550 --> 00:40:11,629
I was slightly upset,

703
00:40:11,630 --> 00:40:12,388
but I'm fine now.

704
00:40:12,389 --> 00:40:13,680
It feels quite freeing,

705
00:40:13,749 --> 00:40:14,919
I make myself busy, too.

706
00:40:16,510 --> 00:40:18,400
I think you are in a good state now.

707
00:40:21,430 --> 00:40:23,119
This one.

708
00:40:23,269 --> 00:40:24,709
It seems like her.

709
00:40:24,710 --> 00:40:27,010
(Weibo text)

710
00:40:27,080 --> 00:40:28,410
(Latte)

711
00:40:29,309 --> 00:40:30,519
No way.

712
00:40:31,869 --> 00:40:32,840
It's not her.

713
00:40:32,910 --> 00:40:34,439
It's the wrong nail color.

714
00:40:57,189 --> 00:40:58,429
Why did I fall asleep?

715
00:40:58,430 --> 00:41:00,119
How long have I been asleep?

716
00:41:01,110 --> 00:41:01,788
Not long.

717
00:41:01,789 --> 00:41:02,469
You can sleep a little longer.

718
00:41:02,470 --> 00:41:03,188
I'll keep looking.

719
00:41:03,189 --> 00:41:04,519
No more sleep.

720
00:41:06,470 --> 00:41:08,160
When I close my eyes,

721
00:41:08,349 --> 00:41:08,989
I am still looking

722
00:41:08,990 --> 00:41:11,039
for her alt account even in my dream.

723
00:41:11,229 --> 00:41:12,919
I'd better look for it awake.

724
00:41:14,229 --> 00:41:15,228
It's too hidden.

725
00:41:15,229 --> 00:41:16,720
We just can't seem to find it.

726
00:41:18,309 --> 00:41:20,079
How about this?

727
00:41:20,269 --> 00:41:21,959
The location is nearby.

728
00:41:22,309 --> 00:41:24,160
Only kittens and puppies' images
are posted.

729
00:41:26,990 --> 00:41:29,039
It's a guy.

730
00:41:44,110 --> 00:41:45,160
Li Shu.

731
00:41:46,829 --> 00:41:48,149
Who are you?

732
00:41:48,150 --> 00:41:49,439
I am Xiang Qian's sister.

733
00:41:50,269 --> 00:41:51,268
I don't know where Gao Ping is.

734
00:41:51,269 --> 00:41:52,360
I'm here to see you.

735
00:41:59,430 --> 00:42:00,479
You must know

736
00:42:00,910 --> 00:42:01,880
Lin Xiao.

737
00:42:02,630 --> 00:42:03,629
We know

738
00:42:03,630 --> 00:42:04,668
all the filthy things you did

739
00:42:04,669 --> 00:42:05,919
with Gao Ping.

740
00:42:06,789 --> 00:42:07,720
Besides,

741
00:42:07,910 --> 00:42:08,708
we found

742
00:42:08,709 --> 00:42:10,149
your alt account on Weibo.

743
00:42:10,150 --> 00:42:11,788
From taking pictures of peony flowers

744
00:42:11,789 --> 00:42:13,388
