747
00:42:17,950 --> 00:42:19,119
I already took screenshots.

748
00:42:19,349 --> 00:42:20,388
In a situation like yours,

749
00:42:20,389 --> 00:42:22,188
I can sue you for fraud.

750
00:42:22,189 --> 00:42:23,919
You can possibly get
a three-year prison sentence.

751
00:42:26,229 --> 00:42:27,519
What do you want?

752
00:42:27,630 --> 00:42:28,999
I'm here to remind you
to return the money.

753
00:42:29,229 --> 00:42:30,308
200,000,

754
00:42:30,309 --> 00:42:31,760
not a single cent less.

755
00:42:32,709 --> 00:42:34,479
We will certainly expose Gao Ping,

756
00:42:34,869 --> 00:42:36,919
the greater the impact, the better.

757
00:42:37,150 --> 00:42:39,109
But if it affects you by then,

758
00:42:39,110 --> 00:42:40,760
don't blame me for not warning you.

759
00:42:41,070 --> 00:42:42,119
Do you understand?

760
00:42:42,189 --> 00:42:43,479
The sooner the better.

